<!-- Optional: Field (container field containing the plug-in). If omitted, uses the current container field in the active table. -->
<!-- The plug-in must be inserted in a container field first. Only .fmx64 (Windows), .fmplugin (macOS), or .fmx (Linux) extensions are supported. ZIP and TAR compressed files cannot be installed. -->
<!-- Use Get(InstalledFMPlugins) or Get(InstalledFMPluginsAsJSON) to check plug-in name, version, and enabled state. -->
<!-- Plug-ins must be enabled in plug-in settings to be recognized. If an update is installed but the plug-in is disabled, the update installs but remains disabled. -->
